OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy throughout the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with showers, these heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes and occasionally forming longer
OL,9,Fspells of rain. Best chance of drier,
OL,10,Fclearer spells in the south. Windy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy for Argyll with
OL,13,Fscattered showers or occasionally
OL,14,Flonger spells of rain. Best of drier
OL,15,Fand brighter spells in the south and
OL,16,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
